full_moon_features.title: Full Moon Features
full_moon_features.description: Full Moon is one of the most popular and prolific independent studios in history with over 550 films in its library as well as several key franchises such as Puppet Master, Demonic Toys, Evil Bong and The Gingerdead Man. Explore the Full Moon universe!

460209.title: Bloodstone: Subspecies 2
460209.description: On the run with the bloodstone, recently bitten Michelle finds herself pursued by an embassy worker, a detective, an anthropologist and the evil Radu.

460210.title: Puppetmaster: Axis Termination
460210.description: To stop the Third Reich and the Nazi war machine from winning World War II and affecting the outcome of the free world, BLADE, JESTER, LEECH WOMAN, PINHEAD and the rest of the indestructible Toulon puppets join forces with the masters of psychic powers! Teaming up with Toulon's bloodthirsty marionettes, these unlikely allies face off against a pack of powerful Nazis and their own clan of malevolent puppets; WEREMACHT, BOMBSHELL and the unstoppable tank-like BLITZKRIEG.

460211.title: Vampire Journals
460211.description: After witnessing the love of his life get turned into one of his own, a vampire with a conscience destroys her, his master and a former protege.

460212.title: Subspecies
460212.description: In modern day Transylvania, three young beauties have stumbled on the path of a suppressed evil from the past that has come back to haunt the present.

460213.title: Castle Freak
460213.description: A father struggles to save his family from the hideous and deformed creature he finds living within the walls of the castle they've just inherited.

460214.title: Dark Angel
460214.description: After managing to escape hell, a woman who is used by dark forces to punish sinners becomes destined for freedom and eventually finds love.

460215.title: Puppetmaster X: Axis Rising
460215.description: The battle is over the war has just begun...After foiling a plot to blow up an American arms plant, DANNY COOGAN and his girlfriend, BETH, quickly find that their troubles have just begun. One of Toulon's mysterious Puppets has been kidnapped by the Nazis, and under the wicked, watchful eye of the occultist COMMANDANT MOEBIUS, the Puppets life-giving serum is synthesized to create a master race of unstoppable soldiers.

460305.title: Devious
460305.description: Some family secrets should stay buried! The mysterious Arkoff family lives in a castle secluded from the outside world, but their beautiful daughter Naomi (Robin Sydney) desperately wants to connect with the outside world. When Naomi invites three outsiders into the castle, they turn out to be deadly art thieves. The thieves are soon given a taste of their own medicine by the castle's protectors. These protectors are empowered by ancient Italian witchcraft and elemental magic. Some know them as SKULL HEADS!

460306.title: Zombie Decadence
460306.description: The Tough Titty is a strip club that's seen better days. Spider has been losing money on his business for years. Now it's finally getting the traffic he's always wanted... unfortunately, most of his patrons are undead.

460326.title: Puppet Master Blitzkrieg: Bunker of Blood 1
460326.description: The most shocking and outrageous moments from the 11-film “Puppet Master” universe are brought together, along with new moments of mayhem.

460328.title: Prehysteria
460328.description: A farmer accidentally brings his kids a bundle of rare eggs that soon hatch into miniature dinosaurs, but the man who found them wants them back.

460329.title: Parasite Dolls
460329.description: A woman in a brutal women's detention center wishes away her troubles to a set of tiny Worry Dolls that crawl into her ear and possess her.

460330.title: Puppetmaster: Axis of Evil
460330.description: At the height of World War II, a young man dreaming of fighting the Nazis soon has a battle of his own when a crate of puppets is unleashed.

460332.title: Lurking Fear
460332.description: A town, plagued by unearthly beings for decades, is the final battleground for a returning heir, criminals after his money, and evil creatures.

460333.title: Killjoy the Demon Clown
460333.description: Four students house sitting for their professor face the worst spring break ever when he raises the demon clown Killjoy and his evil clown friends.

460336.title: Intruder
460336.description: With a murderous, sadistic maniac loose in their grocery store, a group of employees band together to stay alive and expose the killer.

460337.title: Haunted Hollywood
460337.description: A group of sexy women who are looking to party end up in the clutches of the perverse and sadistic ghouls that haunt a notorious mansion.

460339.title: Witchouse
460339.description: A malevolent witch, who wreaked havoc centuries ago, is now being summoned by a twisted and dangerous woman with murderous intentions.

460343.title: Tourist Trap
460343.description: A group of friends stranded at a secluded roadside museum are stalked by a man who uses his telekinetic powers to control the museum’s mannequins.

460611.title: William Shatner's Halloween Frightnight: The Creeps
460611.description: William Shatner hosts this campy horror flick about a mad scientist who brings back Dracula and other iconic monsters, but at half their normal size.

460613.title: Pet Shop
460613.description: Disguised aliens set up a pet shop in a dusty Arizona town, hoping to lure local children with their adorable extraterrestrial critters.

460617.title: The Disembodied
460617.description: Four party girls accidentally unleash the Killer Eye, a disembodied eyeball that will stop at nothing to satisfy its perverse desires.

460618.title: Cannibal Women in the Avocado Jungle of Death
460618.description: A beautiful feminist scientist and her sarcastic trail guide run up against a clan of scantily clad women while out in the wilderness of California.

460619.title: Specters
460619.description: A documentary crew uncover the sinister secrets of a haunted hospital, where they soon find themselves trapped, and tormented by an unspeakable fear.

460620.title: Head of the Family
460620.description: A few unfortunate locals get to know Myron, a giant head on a tiny body, who psychically controls the rest of his even weirder mutant family.

460621.title: Unlucky Charms
460621.description: Five aspiring models try to model a diva’s fashion line on a 24/7 reality show, but end up competing for their lives against four mythical beings.

460622.title: Meridian
460622.description: Two American girls in Italy are drugged and assaulted by an evil magician and his twin who suffer from a curse that turns them into werewolves.

460623.title: The Pit & the Pendulum
460623.description: An innocent woman is accused of witchcraft and dragged before the Spanish Inquisition, which knows no boundaries in making her suffer for her crimes.

460869.title: Jack the Ripper
460869.description: A savage, erotic spin on the infamous serial killer, who murders English prostitutes as retribution for the sins of his street walker mother.

462102.title: Ragdoll
462102.description: A teenage rapper uses his grandmother's magic powers and the help of a murderous ragdoll to seek revenge against those who put her in the hospital.

462103.title: Ooga Booga
462103.description: When a medical student is brutally murdered by a dirty cop, his soul is magically transferred into an action figure named Ooga Booga.

463110.title: Sorority Babes in the Slimeball Bowl-O-Rama
463110.description: A college ritual goes wrong when three sexy sorority girls steal a bowling trophy, releasing a devilish imp who makes their night a living hell.

463111.title: Slave Girls From Beyond
463111.description: Lovely and resourceful Daria and Tisa escape a space gulag only to crash land on a nearby world where a guy in tight pants named Zed is playing The Most Dangerous Game. Zed turns the girls and another guest loose in his jungle preserve to serve as the prey in a mad hunt. Armed only with knives and their wits, the girls must battle their way accross the jungle to a hidden arms cache before Zed catches and kills them.

463117.title: Puppetmaster
463117.description: A group of psychics end up in a battle with a master puppeteer who has discovered the secret of death in the form of five murderous puppets.

463118.title: Trancers
463118.description: A gruff bounty hunter travels back in time to 1980s Los Angeles to stop a twisted criminal who can transform people into zombie-like creatures.

464149.title: Shrunken Heads
464149.description: Inspired by their favorite comic book heroes, young Tommy and his pals take it upon themselves to clean up their menacing neighborhood by busting the local street punks. But the three youths run into big trouble for all their good intentions in the form of Big Mo (Meg Foster), the local crime boss and all around bully. Mo wastes no time in wasting the trio of irritating do-gooders. But Sumatra (Julius Harris), a retired (but still practicing) voodoo specialist revives the boys with a healthy dose of Voodoo mumbo-jumbo. Empowered beyond their wildest dreams, the shrunken trio head out to take on Big Mo and her boys! The film was directed by Danny Elfman's brother!

464150.title: Shadowzone
464150.description: Beyond ALIEN and beyond THE THING comes creatures found only in your deepest nightmares! On the dark side of dreams, a new terror takes shape. There's been a gruesome death at Project Shadowzone but that's just the beginning. A group of NASA hyper-sleep researchers are conducting tests in an abandoned underground facility in the Nevada desert. One subject has died during the test and NASA has sent Captain Hickock to investigate. What he finds is more horrific than the death itself.  Scientists, guided by Dr. Erhart and Dr. Van Fleet have broken the boundaries of dream-state sleep and have tapped into a parallel dimension. The deadly error brings forth an alien life form that decides to stay and prey. The alien being can assume any life form it wants and becomes each person's deepest darkest fear.

464151.title: Killjoy
464151.description: Deep in a gang-infested inner city hell, a ghastly figure is killing off the bad guys and it’s up to a beautiful high school student to stop it.

464153.title: Creepozoids
464153.description: After a nuclear war, a band of deserters flee into the desert only to find an underground lab where a mysterious fluid creates bloodthirsty beasts.

464157.title: Blood Dolls
464157.description: A billionaire inventor secretly hides four beautiful rock & roll singers in a cage at home to play on command while he invents four deadly dolls.

464158.title: Demonic Toys
464158.description: A tough policewoman and five other adults get trapped in a warehouse full of possessed toys that come to life with different murderous specialties.

464159.title: Doctor Mordrid
464159.description: Two sorcerers - one who wants to destroy the earth, the other wants to save it - take their battle into a fourth dimension where only one can win.

465850.title: Deadly Dolls: Deepest Cuts
465850.description: Once more, we follow the mind-bending adventures of a nameless drifter with an impossibly high pain tolerance, who finds himself trapped in the lair of "The Gore Collector", a sadistic curator of carnage who is well past his prime and now seeks an heir to take over his evil operation. Deep within The Gore Collector's "Bunker of Blood", the perverse programmer subjects the man to a non-stop shock treatment of some of the goriest and gruesomest moments from some of Full Moon's most iconic film franchises. Will he survive? DEADLY DOLLS: DEEPEST CUTS features the sickest scenes from classic flicks like BLOOD DOLLS, DOLL GRAVEYARD, DANGEROUS WORRY DOLLS, DEMONIC TOYS and more, mashing them together with macabre music and brand new moments of body-breaking mayhem.

465851.title: Cryptz
465851.description: Things go from bad to worse when aspiring rappers follow a stripper to a mysterious club where the ladies are vampires in disguise.

466610.title: Puppet Master III: Toulon's Revenge
466610.description: A French puppeteer creates an army of bloodthirsty puppets to inflict deadly vengeance on the Nazi henchmen who murdered his beloved wife.

466611.title: Killjoy 2: Deliverance From Evil
466611.description: After a brush with a voodoo priestess, a group of juvenile delinquents find themselves trapped in the woods with a demonic clown called Killjoy.

466612.title: Puppet Master II
466612.description: Paranormal researchers investigate a hotel's murderous past, and instead discover bloodthirsty puppets with a gruesome will to live.

466886.title: Shrieker
466886.description: A young student living as a squatter in an abandoned hospital with her fellow students discovers one of her “roommates” plans to resurrect a demonic killer.

466887.title: Subspecies 3: Bloodlust
466887.description: Evil vampire Radu returns and now he sets his sights on Michelle, who also must contend with Radu’s mother. Fortunately, her sister is coming to help.

467385.title: Gingerdead Man
467385.description: A killer who died in an electric chair comes to life in the form of an adorable yet evil gingerbread man made in the bakery from hell.

468858.title: Murdercycle
468858.description: An alien death machine, with no human emotion, kills to live as it invades the earthy dimension with a mission to destroy the one person in its way.

468943.title: Dr. Moreau's House of Pain
468943.description: When an athlete disappears after going to the notorious Dr. Moreau a rare blood disease, his brother finds he was turned into a man-animal hybrid.

468973.title: The Creeps
468973.description: A mad scientist brings fictional monsters to life in miniature who are hellbent on proving they are just as deadly as their full-size counterparts.

469162.title: Robot Wars
469162.description: Gigantic fighting robots are the last remaining superpower in a post-apocalyptic world, where outlaws will stop at nothing to wield their might.

469310.title: Gingerdead Man 3: Saturday Night Cleaver
469310.description: Gingerdead Man escapes from jail and takes a time machine to disco fever 1976, where no roller-boogie girls or disco dudes are safe from his mayhem.

469612.title: Laserblast
469612.description: When an outcast teenager finds an alien weapon left behind in the desert and goes on a rampage, each laser blast transforms him further into an alien.

469613.title: Killjoy Goes to Hell
469613.description: Banished for failing to commit his last crime, demonic clown Killjoy is left to face the devil in hell’s courtroom and face trial by combat.

469615.title: Crash and Burn
469615.description: In 2030, computers have put the world into total poverty and have been banned, but a man and his granddaughter still fight cyborgs from the desert.

469873.title: Retro Puppet Master
469873.description: An origins tale of a 19th century demon who places the souls of the dying into inanimate objects, putting a puppeteer, sorcerer and woman in his web.

469874.title: Puppet Master 5
469874.description: A doctor’s plans to sell the source of puppet animation for war sets him in a deadly battle against the original Puppet Master and an evil pharaoh.

469875.title: Necropolis
469875.description: A Satanic witch killed in the 1600s comes back to the 1980s, posing as a biker babe and taking the souls of crooks, prostitutes and drug addicts

470098.title: Trancers II: The Return of Jack Deth
470098.description: 6 years after a time cop returns home from battling future alien zombies, his settled life is turned upside down when a mad scientists creates more.

470099.title: Gingerdead Man 2: Bakery of Blood
470099.description: A man inherits his father’s struggling film studio and starts making schlock films, but the Gingerdead Man is on his way to the set for bloody murder.

470100.title: Hideous!
470100.description: A doctor acquires mutant-human terrors and sees his latest find come alive and replicate ferocious freaks, while its creator and the FBI close in.

471246.title: Killjoy's Psycho Circus
471246.description: A demon clown wreaking havoc on Earth becomes hunted by other members of hell who have devised a plan to trap its spirit and drag it back to hell.

472178.title: The Day Time Ended
472178.description: When a supernova tears a hole in time, a family find their desert dream home under assault by aliens and prehistoric monstrosities.

474405.title: Vampire Slaughter: Eaten Alive
474405.description: A collection of gory horror film moments as seen by three horror movie misfits who sail the Blood Sea after fighting a tribe of island albino vampires.

474406.title: Psycho Sideshow: Demon Freaks
474406.description: Horror film studio Full Moon returns with shocking moments from their catalog of films, hosted from an animated, terrifying amusement park from hell.

474409.title: Magic in the Mirror
474409.description: The looking glass Alice went through has a side that’s a fantasy world that other beings guard, but a little girl finds her imaginary friends there.

474417.title: Evil Bong 2: Devil's Harvest
474417.description: The bizarre side-effects of a weed session with Evil Bong leads a group of pals to South America for a cure, but deadly powerful King Bong is waiting.

474418.title: Evil Bong 3: Reefer Madness
474418.description: A galactic stoner comedy about survivors of a battle with King Bong whose Venice Beach head shop gets them enslaved by an alien’s sexy weed strain.

474419.title: Evil Bong 420
474419.description: A man’s escape from Evil Bong’s world of weed leads him to open a 420-friendly, topless bowling alley but his enemies have plans of their own.

474422.title: Demonic Toys 2: Personal Demons
474422.description: An evil doctor and collector of freak oddities gets help from a deranged couple to collect demonic dolls and catch an evil puppet now in human form.

474423.title: Prehysteria 2
474423.description: An energetic band of tiny pygmy dinosaurs return after escaping from their hatch farm, ending up at a rich, lonely boy’s house for fun and trouble.

478157.title: Invisible: The Chronicles of Benjamin Knight
478157.description: After a lab accident, an American scientist gains the superpower of invisibility. Can he take control of his newfound ability to save the day?

478158.title: Evil Bong 666
478158.description: When a sacrifice opens a portal to Hell, our oddball heroes are returned to Earth. Motivations are not always what they seem, and tensions are high.

478159.title: Netherworld
478159.description: After inheriting a mansion in Louisiana, a young man meets a series of bizarre characters who have a connection to his late father.

478161.title: The Werewolf Reborn!
478161.description: The townspeople of a mysterious, isolated village seem to be under a kind of spell, which leads a young woman to investigate some odd lunar events.

478162.title: Kraa! the Sea Monster
478162.description: The king of monsters attacks earth! Luckily, Planet Patrol allies with mankind to stop the plans of an evil master and give Earth a fighting chance.

478163.title: Arcade
478163.description: All the kids in town are dying to play an addictive new video game. A teen discovers that the game has a mysterious and dangerous twist.

478164.title: Prison of the Dead
478164.description: Former high school friends have a reunion in an abandoned witches' prison. All is well until three dead executioners come back to life.

478165.title: Bad Channels
478165.description: A rock ’n’ roll-loving alien takes over a local radio station, all the while scheming to kidnap beautiful women back to his home planet.

478225.title: Puppet Master 4: The Demon
478225.description: Our favorite living puppets battle their most menacing enemy yet: a horde of terrifying creatures known as "Totems," who were sent by a demon.

478267.title: Sideshow
478267.description: A group of high school students discover that the local sideshow is more than a cheap thrill when an evil ringmaster grants them their wishes.

478271.title: Hell Asylum
478271.description: A desperate producer sends five models into a haunted old building for a chance to win a million bucks. No amount of money is worth what’s in store.

478272.title: Seedpeople
478272.description: A quiet town is invaded by plants from outer space. These evil greens can turn humans into walking seed carriers. Can they be stopped?

480555.title: Deathbed
480555.description: A successful illustrator makes a rare bed the centerpiece of her home, but devious terrors and memories soon awaken from the bed to invade her life.

483341.title: Gingerdead Man vs Evil Bong
483341.description: An evil bong vs an insane living cookie? What can go wrong? It's a War of the Colossal Freaks when serial killing cookie, Gingerdead Man, tracks down the lone survivor of his murderous rampage, Sarah Leigh (Robin Sydney), to take care of unfinished business. But his devious plans go up in smoke when Sarah meets Larnell (John Patrick Jordan), who has a pint-sized problem of his own. The Evil Bong, EeBee, has been unleashed once again. Bodies begin to pile up as Gingerdead Man carves a path for them. Their only salvation is to turn to help from the dastardly Bong. It's one tough cookie versus one bad trip mother when the two Titans of Terror hash out a war in the Bong World. The stakes have never been higher.

484422.title: Evil Bong: High-5!
484422.description: Humanity’s in for a harsh buzz when EeBee the Evil Bong plots world domination and sends a band of buds on a weed-fueled adventure.

487260.title: Young Blood, Fresh Meat
487260.description: An aspiring model comes to L.A. to pursue film stardom, but a sexy vampire recruits her to become an escort before making her part of a vampire coven.

487262.title: The Killer Eye
487262.description: A mad scientist performs an experiment on a dead homeless man’s eyeball, which rises into the air and now lives to scope out and kill young women.

487264.title: Reel Exposure
487264.description: John Carradine hosts this grindhouse tribute to 40 of the most lurid exploitation films ever, each shortened into 3 minutes of their best scenes.

487268.title: Ravenwolf Towers
487268.description: A high-rise complex that was once home to Hollywood’s elite is now run by an inbred family hiding terrifying secrets and renting to freak guests.

487270.title: Mega Scorpions
487270.description: Toxic waste in a town has turned scorpions into 6-foot killers, which a teen has seen for herself, but no one believes her and they're coming to feed.

487278.title: Fists of Fury
487278.description: Martial arts mayhem explodes onscreen as a seductive sensei presents some of the best cinematic black-belt moves – and fails – ever filmed.

487280.title: Filmgore
487280.description: ‘70s slasher films get their violent, sensational due in this feature-length collection of maniacal scenes hosted by Elvira, Mistress of the Dark.

487282.title: Evil Bong 777
487282.description: Evil Bong returns from her time in sexy hell and heads to Las Vegas with ganja-soaked, raunchy intentions as well as a fling with stud-puppet Hellvis.

487291.title: Zombiethon
487291.description: The living dead come alive in this documentary tribute to the creepiest undead in filmdom, from space zombies to others from all walks of death.

491325.title: Zombie Lust: Night Flesh - Bunker of Blood 6
491325.description: Comprised of clips from midnight movies, this ode to blood-and-guts is full of flesh-eating zombies, exploding heads and ghoulish monsters.

491327.title: Trancers 5: Sudden Deth
491327.description: Future lawman Jack Deth must find his way home from the other-dimensional world of Orpheus, where magic works and trancers are the ruling class.

491329.title: Witchouse II
491329.description: When a strange, old house in Transylvania is razed by developers, unmarked graves are discovered, people start dying, and a professor investigates.

491331.title: Trancers 4:Jack of Swords
491331.description: Lost somewhere in the future, lawman Jack learns he’s lost his wife to another and lands in a new, dangerous dimension, where evil Lord Caliban rules.

491335.title: Oblivion 2
491335.description: In an alien-western world, a sheriff, a gambler, and a bounty hunter face off in a showdown over a precious mineral mine and who will rule the galaxy.

491337.title: Killjoy's Carnage Caravan - Bunker of Blood 7
491337.description: The 7th installment of the ‘Bunker of Blood’ series where a group of psychotic surgeons experimenting on innocent victims are hunted for revenge.

491339.title: Doll Graveyard
491339.description: An abused girl, buried with 4 dolls 100 years earlier by her evil father, possesses the dolls found by a bullied teenager and has them fight for him.

491341.title: Decadent Evil II
491341.description: Vampire Sugar and her boyfriend travel with a mutant to heal his son, but a strip club full of wicked creatures plan to sacrifice Sugar to their king.

491345.title: Curse of the Puppet Master
491345.description: The evil puppets are back in a traveling doll circus run by a puppet carver whose monstrous schemes will bring out their sure fight to the death.

491347.title: Butcher’s Bake Off: Hell’s Kitchen - Bunker of Blood: Chapter 8
491347.description: Splatter cinema installment about a psychotic surgeon whose escape has a team of evil freaks chasing him out of parallel time and into the real world.

491349.title: Hard Rock Candy
491349.description: Three women who once had it all want revenge, but it will be a tall and hot order when a mysterious millionaire offers to finance their music tour.

492173.title: Bada$$ Mothaf**kas
492173.description: Through the use of movie clips and trailers, actor Fred Williamson presents the history of early blaxploitation films of the 1970s.

495944.title: Witchouse 3: Demon Fire
495944.description: After escaping an abusive relationship, a young woman and her friends unintentionally summon a dark and dangerous witch known as Lilith.

495948.title: Spellcaster
495948.description: Winning a trip to Italy proved to be the worst thing to ever happen to a group of young people, as they're picked off one by one.

495952.title: Puppet Master: The Legacy
495952.description: A ruthless interrogator uses violence and threats to extract information from a man with a connection to mysterious and powerful puppets.

495954.title: Petrified
495954.description: A mummified alien is reanimated by a dead man's blood. With the creature on the loose in a hospital, patients have little chance of escape.

495958.title: Cemetery High
495958.description: Creepy guys are hunted down by a group of revenge-driven, well-armed high school girls who are tired of being treated like objects.

495962.title: Demonicus
495962.description: After a young man is possessed by the spirit of a demon gladiator named Tyranus, he begins to prey on a group of unknowing students.

495964.title: The Alchemist
495964.description: A waitress meets an alchemist in the woods. He can't help but notice that she bares a striking resemblance to his murdered wife from 100 years ago.

496302.title: Trancers 6
496302.description: This sixth installment of the Trancers saga wakes up time traveling Jack Deth in his daughter’s body to save the world from the most lethal breed yet.

500825.title: Horrific
500825.description: Three bone-chilling stories pulled from classic films deliver three horrifying fates: a deadly seance, a mad experiment, and an unholy sacrifice.

500827.title: Possessed
500827.description: Witches’ brew is on the menu in this terrifying trilogy of spells, demons, and black magic, all guaranteed to have you reaching for that eye of newt!

500829.title: Tomb of Terror
500829.description: Three chilling tales are unearthed from the mausoleum of classic films, featuring hellspawn terror and otherworldly horror from beyond the grave!

500831.title: Urban Evil
500831.description: Horror hits the hood in this trilogy of terror featuring a zombie-wielding record producer, a mystical doll, and an old high school with a curse.

500833.title: DevilDolls
500833.description: Padlock the toy chest and double-bolt the attic because these three tales of demonic playthings will absolutely ruin your childhood.

500835.title: Remote
500835.description: A 13-year-old boy, obsessed with making remote-control toys, puts up a fight when trapped in a vacant model house with three dimwit prison escapees.

507763.title: The Dead Reborn
507763.description: Three terrifying tales are told as the dead rise to walk and stalk the Earth, spawned from strange occult rituals to outbreaks of biochemical viruses.

507766.title: Mr. Galactic
507766.description: Alien sightings in a Connecticut town turn out to be lusty alien man who won a trip to Earth on a game show in space, with sexy women as his prize.

507768.title: Haunted Dollhouse
507768.description: A horror anthology series revolving around three terrifying chapters of the undead and supernatural taking their power back from the living.

507770.title: Alien Arsenal
507770.description: After two nerdy high school teens find a stash of forgotten alien armor and weapons in their high school’s basement, they become cyber superheroes.

514013.title: Tales From the Grave
514013.description: Three stories paint a gruesome picture of survival in horrific circumstances, including zombies, the paranormal, and one powerful witch.

514015.title: Planet Patrol
514015.description: A teenage galactic patrol squad faces dinosaur combat, scorpion tanks, and an epic battle, as they confront an evil villain and his nasty minions.

514022.title: Assault of the Killer Bimbos
514022.description: When two go-go dancers are framed for murder by a sleazy gangster, they begin a wild ride, picking up a waitress on the way toward Mexico and freedom.

514868.title: William Shatner's Full Moon Frightnight: Head of the Family
514868.description: The giant-headed Myron Stackpool and his creepy clan are always up for some freaky experiments involving locals, who may just lose their heads.

514926.title: William Shatner's Full Moon Fright Night: Hideous!
514926.description: Meet Dr. Lorca, a collector of biological oddities. But when he acquires a mutant born of toxic waste, his whole world is threatened.

517951.title: I, Vampire
517951.description: Passionate and sensual members of the undead are featured in three tales of blood-thirsting immortals searching for ultimate power and eternal love.

518240.title: Monsters Gone Wild!
518240.description: Take a look into B-movie master Charles Band’s low-budget horror flick repertoire, which includes countless monsters, vampires, wizards, and ghouls.

521941.title: Beanstalk
521941.description: When a young boy discovers a box full of magical green beans, he plants a beanstalk which leads to an exciting adventure in the sky.

521943.title: To Love a Ghost
521943.description: This errotic romance tale tells of a novelist who travels to a haunted European castle, which provides an intensely inspirational force.

521945.title: The Panther Squad
521945.description: A fearless commando leads her squad of powerful female mercenaries to take on a terrorist organization set on ending space exploration.

528448.title: William Shatner's Full Moon Fright Night: Killjoy
